chi  lubert stryer  david f wilson  bruce m alberts  c fred fox  james e dahlberg  mark ptashne  joan a steitz  robert g roeder  charles r cantor  christopher t walsh  phillip a sharp  roger d kornberg  harold m weintraub  richard axel  david v goeddel  gerald m rubin  james e rothman  jacqueline k barton  peter walter  michael m cox  george l mclendon  peter g schultz  william degrado  stuart l schreiber  peter s kim  jeremy m berg  gregory l verdine  alanna schepartz  john kuriyan  chaitan khosla  xiaodong wang  jennifer doudna  kevan m shokat  andreas matouschek  benjamin cravatt iii  dewey g mccafferty  linda hsiehwilson  anna k mapp  paul j hergenrother  scott k silverman  alice y ting  nathanael gray  christopher j chang  matthew d disney  yi tang  minkui luo  elizabeth nolan  howard hang  v t e fellows of the royal society elected in  fellows alan astbury alan baddeley michael burdekin david crighton lennart carleson tim cluttonbrock richard crowther howard dalton geoffrey dearnaley richard r ernst martin evans ian fleming edward fraenkel richard friend christopher garrett keith glover michael george hall roger heathbrown john hughes robin irvine patricia jacobs franz daniel kahn michael joseph kelly kevin kendall trevor lamb sydney leach angus macintyre michael neuberger ian newton colin patterson colin pillinger ghillean prance edward reynolds john rhodes jim smith brian geoffrey spratt david j stevenson bruce william stillman andrew james thomson peter john twin ae walsby john white foreign bruce alberts jeanmarie lehn motoo kimura edwin ernest salpeter molecular and cellular biology portal authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbn data ndl  nkc jn bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebrucealbertsoldid categories  birthsmembers of the united states national academy of sciencesliving peopleamerican biochemistsharvard university alumniprinceton university facultyuniversity of california san francisco fa